  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install Nettle by running the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Disable installing the static library:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed -i '/^install-here/ s/install-static//' Makefile</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install &amp;&amp;
chmod -v 755 /usr/lib/libhogweed.so /usr/lib/libnettle.so</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

